    IMS Daily Northern Hemisphere Snow and Ice Analysis v1.2+v1.3

Start date:
January, 2004

End date:
December, 2015

Temporal resolution:
daily

Spatial resolution:
4 X 4 sq.km

Unit: 
snow/snow+land

